headline: Looking at the Narrative for Seagate as Analyst Targets Shift with AI Storage Demand
summary: Seagate Technology Holdings has seen analysts significantly boost their consensus price target, rising from $204.35 to $241.10. This shift reflects increased optimism about the company's potential, particularly as demand for AI-driven storage solutions grows. Stay tuned to learn how you can continue tracking these evolving perspectives and what they mean for Seagate’s stock outlook in the future.
